title: The Greatest
lyrics:
They call me the greatest

And they're being sarcastic
They're being sarcastic
Oh, I'm taking names

But I'm not doing much

G-O-A-T

They're being sarcastic



They call me the greatest

But those tears can be quiet

So I listen close

I listen close

Yes I'm taking notes

But those notes aren't helping

It washes away

It washes away
